verbose_text: SFN treatment resulted in a decrease in mRNA levels of CCNA2 (cyclin A2), CCNB1 (cyclin B1), CCNB2 (cyclin B2), CCND3 (cyclin D3) and CCNE1 (cyclin E1) in MCF-7 and MDA-MB-231 cells, CCND1 (cyclin D1) in SK-BR-3 cells, and CCND2 (cyclin D2) and CCNH (cyclin H) in MDA-MB-231 cells.
